see at night.</li><li>Be careful on <b>poorly lit streets</b> and alleys.</li><li><b>Keep your distance</b> — more drink-drivers in the evening. Be predictable, don&rsquo;t weave.</li><li><b>Don&rsquo;t drink and ride</b> — the strictest offence. If you drink, take <a href="baik-vs-grab-en.html">Grab/taxi</a>.</li></ul><h2>Nha Trang by night on a bike is great</h2><p>If all is well, night riding in Nha Trang is a treat: the Tran Phu seafront, the night market, the lights, seaside cafes. Where to go — see <a href="marshruty-nyachang-en.html">routes around Nha Trang</a>.</p><h2>Where we come in</h2><p>At night the <b>electrics and lights</b> matter most — and we <b>service and check the lights</b> before sale. So the bike is ready for evening rides. How to care for it — <a href="uhod-za-baikom-en.html">scooter care</a>.</p><p style="margin-top:24px"><a href="catalog-en.html" class="btn btn-wa">See bikes &rarr;</a> <a href="marshruty-nyachang-en.html" class="btn btn-tg" style="margin-left:8px">Where to ride &rarr;</a></p></div></section><footer><div class="wrap"><div class="fgrid"><div><h4>50cc bikes in Nha Trang</h4><p>Honest 50cc bikes (scooters). Police-checked, gentle mileage, serviced, warranty and 50% buy-back.</p><div class="pay"><span>₫ VND</span><span>$ USD</span><span>USDT</span><span>Cash</span></div></div><div><h4>Menu</h4><a href="catalog-en.html">Catalog</a><a href="vykup-en.html">Buy-back</a><a href="kak-kupit-en.html">How to buy</a><a href="blog-en.html">Articles</a><a href="o-nas-en.html">About</a></div><div><h4>Contacts</h4><a href="https://wa.me/84386818874">WhatsApp</a><a href="https://t.me/babaskin_o">Telegram</a><a href="https://instagram.com/bike50cc_nha_trang">Instagram</a><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/jsxikqy9AZMNtmAE6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Maps</a><p>Nha Trang · daily</p></div></div><div class="copy">© 2026 50cc bikes in Nha Trang. All rights reserved.</div></div></footer></body></html>